[p 
	"A yet another quest to save a pixel princess! This time the princess looks like a blob, though.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"The game in question is 
	[em 
		"A Boy and His Blob - The Rescue of Princess Blobette
	]em
	". If you enjoy the 
	[a class=intlink href=/883M 
		"NES prequel
	]a
	", you will probably enjoy this one too. There is only one level, 
	[a class=extlink href=http://www.vgmaps.com/Atlas/GB-GBC/index.htm#BoyAndHisBlobInTheRescueOfPrincessBlobette rel=nofollow 
		"the castle
	]a
	", which consists of 104 (8x13) screens filled with hazardous puzzles. The gameplay is very non-linear and there are many ways to save the trapped princess. This is the fastest route I was able to find.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"This movie has been available at my 
	[a class=intlink href=/Aqfaq 
		"userpage
	]a
	" for some time. I submitted it now, because I have no intention to improve it and it is a funny movie anyway. Thanks to LSK for feedback. 
	$LF
]p
